{"tid":812255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奶共港豬成貿易戰炮灰】俾東莞政府針對仲要被美帝加徵關稅！","createTime":"2018-09-09T13:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T13:20:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e741585df15d0541e3bce0660901b7f8e3d4456","tid":812255,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180909/58650679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58650679&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=27981a59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F58650679&h=9a6d4446\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180909/58650679</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536253789_45b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536253789_45b0.jpg&h=0c80e2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰升溫，美國總統特朗普再打一槍，中國製造勢將成大輸家！在東莞設廠29年的香港廠商劉達邦，近半年就不斷自問：「我哋仲做嚟做咩呢？」當初港商在東莞盡受禮遇，近十幾年生意不景，最近更成為政府針對的目標，2年前近8萬間的港資廠商，今年只剩下約2.5萬間，偏偏「屋漏偏逢連夜雨」，如今還要面對美國對2,000億元中國貨品增收關稅的壓力。<br />\n劉達邦出口的鋁製品及塗噴都在這份清單中，隨時失去1/4生意，令他意興欄柵，留低繼續做，還被同行取笑。是進，是退？慘成貿易戰炮灰的港商要如何「求生」？即刻睇片！"}]}